html:
Foreign ownership in Indian banks &gt;

India&#39;s central bank RBI <a href="/RBI" title="ReserveBankOfIndia">@RBI</a> granted approval to Abu Dhabi-based Emirates NBD Bank (PJSC) to buy up to 74% stake in Bombay-based RBL Bank Ltd.  <a href="https://www.bseindia.com/xml-data/corpfiling/AttachLive/5a33594e-473d-4942-b78f-10ff91368eee.pdf">bseindia.com/xml-data/corpfi…</a>

The RBI approval is subject to clearance from Govt of India and SEBI.

